7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Linear and Monday.com AI share a solid foundation of core features including Task Management, Ai Assistant, Collaboration, Automation. On the other hand, Monday.com AI uniquely offers Calendar, giving it an edge for users who prioritize this area. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Linear holds an overall score of 9/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10, while Monday.com AI scores 8/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both Linear and Monday.com AI offer flexible pricing models. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Linear's free tier and Monday.com AI's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
